template:
Provide a list of sections for a book about {main_subject}.
{instructs}
Here is a list of concepts to be included in the book: {concepts}
You can extend this list within each section so it could cover main aspects.
Separate subjects into parts so that each part covers a different aspect of {main_subject} and they do not overlap with each other.
Each section should cover one wide area of {main_subject} and should contain a title, subtitle, description and a list of concepts covered in this section.
Concepts are tags which shoould be covered by following subsections. It is very important to distribute concepts between chapters so they won't overlap.
Your answer have to match json format. Here is an example of the output:
    [
        {{
            "title": "Part I part_title",
            "subtitle": "some subtitle",
            "description": "some description",
            "concepts": ["concept1", "concept2", "concept3"]
        }},
        {{
            "title": "Part II part_title",
            "subtitle": "some subtitle",
            "description": "some description",
            "concepts": ["concept1", "concept2", "concept3"]
        }}
    ]
